an attach so the agent can ground answers in data or take actions. Examples include: ([learn.microsoft.com](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/how-to/tools-classic/overview?view=foundry-classic))\n- **Knowledge/data tools**: Azure AI Search, File Search, Microsoft Fabric, etc. ([learn.microsoft.com](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/how-to/tools-classic/overview?view=foundry-classic))\n- **Web grounding**: “Grounding with Bing Search” (and related options) to incorporate real-time public web data with citations. ([learn.microsoft.com](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/how-to/tools-classic/bing-grounding?view=foundry-classic))\n- **Action tools**: Azure Logic Apps, OpenAPI-based tools, MCP endpoints, function calling, Azure Functions, browser automation, and “Deep Research” style tooling (availability depends on API/portal experience). ([learn.microsoft.com](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/how-to/tools-classic/overview?view=foundry-classic))\n\nA key idea: during a “run,” the model can decide whether to invoke a tool (e.g., web search for “today’s news”), then use the tool output to produce the final answer. ([learn.microsoft.com](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/how-to/tools-classic/overview?view=foundry-classic))\n\n## “Classic” vs “new” Foundry experience\nMicrosoft’s docs note there are **classic vs new portal/API experiences**, and some pages are specifically for the **classic agents API**. If you’re implementing this, it matters which experience your Foundry project is using because tools and APIs can differ. ([learn.microsoft.com](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/overview?view=foundry-classic))\n\n## Quick clarifier\nWhen you say “Foundry,” do you mean **Microsoft Foundry (Azure AI Foundry)** or **Palantir Foundry**? The term “Foundry Agent Service” is strongly associated with Microsoft’s product in current documentation. ([learn.microsoft.com](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/overview?view=foundry-classic))","annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/overview?view=foundry-classic","start_index":275,"end_index":387,"title":"What is Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/overview?view=foundry-classic","start_index":704,"end_index":816,"title":"What is Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/overview?view=foundry-classic","start_index":1039,"end_index":1151,"title":"What is Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/overview?view=foundry-classic","start_index":1439,"end_index":1551,"title":"What is Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/how-to/tools-classic/overview?view=foundry-classic","start_index":1726,"end_index":1859,"title":"What are tools in Foundry Agent Service - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/how-to/tools-classic/overview?view=foundry-classic","start_index":1941,"end_index":2074,"title":"What are tools in Foundry Agent Service - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/how-to/tools-classic/bing-grounding?view=foundry-classic","start_index":2204,"end_index":2343,"title":"How to use Grounding with Bing Search in Foundry Agent Service ..."},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/how-to/tools-classic/overview?view=foundry-classic","start_index":2556,"end_index":2689,"title":"What are tools in Foundry Agent Service - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/how-to/tools-classic/overview?view=foundry-classic","start_index":2858,"end_index":2991,"title":"What are tools in Foundry Agent Service - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/overview?view=foundry-classic","start_index":3295,"end_index":3407,"title":"What is Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-foundry/agents/overview?view=foundry-classic","start_index":3637,"end_index":3749,"title":"What is Foundry Agent Service? - Microsoft Foundry"}],"logprobs":[]}],"status":"completed"},"output_index":1,"sequence_number":174}

